cc:Work.dc:title: Property/PropertyBuilder Class Hierarchy
cc:Work.dc:description: A class diagram showing the Property/PropertyBuilder hierarchy of interfaces, classes, and traits in the VCardTools PHP library as introduced in Milestone 0.9.3. Multiple inheritance via PHP interfaces is used to reproduce the complex RFC 6350 property behaviors while PHP traits provide the implementation inheritance to reduce code duplication. The Property and PropertyBuilder hierarchies closely mirror each other with each pair of Property/PropertyBuilder tightly coupled.

flowRoot.flowPara: Property/PropertyBuilder hierarchies closely mirror each other.
Traits are used internally to reuse code within the hierarchy. Most traits not shown.
Interfaces and traits used as mix-ins to simulate multiple inheritance.
